quran[50]{c,v,t}:
  15,50,Empa kotlo Ea Ka ke kotlo e mahlonoko
  15,51,U be u ba bolelle ka baeti ba Abrahama
  15,52,"Kamoo ba ileng ba buoa le eena kateng mohla baneng ba mo etetse, ha ba re: “Khotso.” A re: “Ruri re’a le ts’aba.”"
  15,53,"Ba re: “U se ts’ohe! Hobane Re u tliselitse litaba tse molemo tsa mora ea apesitsoeng bohlale.”"
  15,54,"A re: “Le ka tlisa litaba tse molemo ho ‘na tsa mora nakong ea botsofali ba ka? Li sa na le eng litaba tsa lona tse molemo?”"
  15,55,"Ba re: “Re u tliselitse litaba tse molemo e le ka ‘nete. Kahoo u se ke oa nyahama.”"
  15,56,"Abrahama a re: “Ke mang ea ka nyahamelang Mohau oa Mong`a hae haese feela ba khelohileng tseleng?”"
  15,57,"A re: “Joale ke le feng lebaka la lona, lona baromuoa ba Allah?”"
  15,58,"Ba re: “Re romeletsoe ho batho bohle ba oetseng sebeng"
  15,59,Ntle le lelapa la lota. Re tla ba pholosa kaofela
  15,60,"Ntle feela le mosali oa Lota, eo Re ikholisitseng hore o tla ba har’a ba tla salla morao.”"
  15,61,Hoba baromuoa ba fihle lelapeng la Lota
  15,62,"A re: “Le shebahala le le batho ba sa tsebahaleng ho ‘na.”"
  15,63,"Eaba ba re: “E, re mpa re u tliselitse seo ba bangata ba nang le khoao malebana le sona"
  15,64,"Re u tliselitse ‘nete, rona re ba boleli ba ‘nete"
  15,65,"U tsamae ka khitla le ba ntlo ea hau, uena u ba qhobe. Ho se be le’a mong oa lona ea tla hetla morao, empa le ee moo le laetsoeng ho ea teng.”"
  15,66,"Ke kamoo re ileng ra mo hlakisetsa taelo kateng, e le hore mesalla ea ba sebeng e tle e lahleheloe ke likamano esale hosasa"
  15,67,Baahi ba motse oo ba ile ba tla ka nyakallo e kholo ha ba utloa litaba tsa baeti bana
  15,68,"Lota a re: “Ke baeti ba ka. Kahoo le se ntlotlolle"
  15,69,"Empa le ts’abe Allah, le se nts’oabise!”"
  15,70,"Ba re: “Na ha Re’a ka Ra u hanela ho phomosetsa mong le mong?”"
  15,71,"A re: “Barali ba ka ke bana, haeba le tlameha ho ba nyala.”"
  15,72,"Ruri ka bophelo ba hau, ba tlankelletse ka botlaopa nyakallong eo ea bona katamelong ea lefu"
  15,73,Ke moo ba ileng ba ripitloa ke ho qhoma ho ts’abehang esale ka meso
  15,74,"Re ile ra ba menola le hona ho ba subuhlellanya, eaba Re ba nesetsa sebabole sa manyeta a besitsoeng"
  15,75,Bonang! Ruri kahar’a tsena ke lits’upiso ho ba utloisisang mats’oao
  15,76,Metse eo e ne e le pel’a ‘mila hantle o ntseng o tsamauoa
  15,77,Bonang! Ruri kahar’a sena ke sesupo ho ba kholoang
  15,78,"Le Balekane ba Moru, ene e le baetsalibe"
  15,79,Re ile Ra iphetetsa ho bona; etsoe le bona ba ntse ba le pel’a ‘mila o moholo o totobetseng ho ka bonoa
  15,80,"Le Balekane ba Al-hijr, ba ile ba latola baromuoa ba Rona"
  15,81,"Re ile Ra ba neha lits’enolo tsa Rona, empa ba ile ba phehella ho li nyahlatsa"
  15,82,"Ba ile ba ipetlela melingoana ka majoe a moralla, moo a ntseng a ituletse teng ka paballeho"
  15,83,Empa ho reketla ho ile ha ba nanola esale ka matjeke
  15,84,Tsohle tseo ba neng ba li etsa ha li’a ka tsa ba tsoela molemo
  15,85,"Ha re’a hlola maholimo le lefats’e le tsohle tse teng lipakeng tsa ona haese ka ‘nete. Ruri Hora e’a tla. Kahoo, bats’oarele ka bokhabane"
  15,86,"Ruri Mong`a hau! Ke `Mopi, Ea Tsebang tsohle"
  15,87,Re u nehile litemana tse supileng tse pheta-phetiloeng hammoho le Qura’n ea Sebele
  15,88,"U se penye mahlo a hau malebana le tseo re li apesitseng ba bang har’a bona: li se u koatise: u mpe u lepeletse mapheeo a hau ho ba kholoang"
  15,89,"Ebe u re: “Ruri ke mohlokomelisi ea hlakileng ea se nang ts’ekamelo,”"
  15,90,Joaloka ha re kile ra romella ho ba arolang
  15,91,Joaloka ha Qura’n e ranthantsoe
  15,92,"Kahoo, ka Mong`a hau, Re tla biletsa boikarabellong"
  15,93,Mabapi le liketso tsa bona
  15,94,"Ka hona phatlalatsa ponts’eng seo u se laetsoeng, o be u furalle ba kopanyang Allah le melimo ea bohata"
  15,95,Re lekane ho u sirelelitsa khahlano le basomi
  15,96,"Ba kopanyang Allah le melingoana: Empa haufinyane ba tla rua tsebo"
  15,97,Re tseba hantle kamoo pelo ea hau e utloang bohloko kateng ke seo ba se buoang
  15,98,"Empa u keteke lithoriso tsa Mong`a hau, u be har’a ba ithapalatsang ka lerato"
  15,99,U sebeletse Mong`a hau ho fihlela u le makhatheng a lefu